'''2builders2tools'''（2b2t）是一個《[[我的世界|我的世界]]》伺服器，於2010年12月建立。它是《我的世界》最古老的「[[無政府|無政府]]」伺服器{{Efn|在《我的世界》中，無政府伺服器是指伺服器近乎沒有規則，也不會封鎖玩家。<ref name="celebspulse">{{Cite web |url=https://celebspulse.com/4-oldest-minecraft-servers-and-why-they-matter/ |title=4 Oldest Minecraft Servers And Why They Matter |date=October 19, 2019 |website=Celebs Pulse |last=Peng |first=Mei |department=Culture |language=en-US |access-date=March 3, 2020 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303063238/https://celebspulse.com/4-oldest-minecraft-servers-and-why-they-matter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}<ref name="mainsite">{{Cite web |url=http://2b2t.org |title=2b2t.org |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130318022710/http://2b2t.org/ |archive-date=2013-03-18 |access-date=2020-01-06 }}</ref><ref name="newsweek">{{Cite news |last=Kiberd |first=Roisin |url=https://www.newsweek.com/2016/09/23/minecraft-anarchy-server-2b2t-will-kill-you-498946.html |title=The Minecraft Server That Will Kill You 1,000 Times |date=2016-09-15 |work=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]] |access-date=2019-09-09 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014024243/https://www.newsweek.com/2016/09/23/minecraft-anarchy-server-2b2t-will-kill-you-498946.html |archive-date=2019-10-14 }}</ref><ref name="kotaku">{{Cite news |last=Guthrie |first=Robert |url=https://kotaku.com/minecrafts-worst-server-is-at-war-with-youtube-1786999271 |title=The Denizens of Minecraft's 'Worst' Server Are At War With YouTube |date=2016-09-23 |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |access-date=2019-09-09 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329164051/https://kotaku.com/minecrafts-worst-server-is-at-war-with-youtube-1786999271 |archive-date=2019-03-29 }}</ref>，也是所有伺服器中第二古老的。此外，2b2t的世界是遊戲中運行時間最長的未更改的地圖之一，自創建以來從未重置過<ref name="celebspulse"/><ref name="vice">{{Cite news |last=Paul |first=Andrew |url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/xywekq/the-worst-place-in-minecraft |title=The Worst Place in Minecraft |date=October 5, 2015 |work=[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] |department=Tech |access-date=September 9, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014214406/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/xywekq/the-worst-place-in-minecraft |archive-date=2019-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="subreddit">{{Cite web |url=https://www.reddit.com/r/2b2t/ |title=Official website sidebar |website=[[Reddit|Reddit]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222192623/https://www.reddit.com/r/2b2t/ |archive-date=2019-12-22 |access-date=December 12, 2019 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於伺服器的無政府性質，毀壞（griefing）{{Efn|毀壞是指某個玩家未經批准蓄意破壞或污損他人的建築物。<ref name="newsweek" />}}和使用外掛經常出現<ref name="analogies">{{Cite web |url=https://www.academia.edu/34446985 |title=Analogies of Religious Violence in Minecraft: A Case Study of 2b2t |last=Apostolacus |first=Katherine |date=December 12, 2016 |website={{tsl|en|Academia.edu|}} |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191124220659/https://www.academia.edu/34446985/Analogies_of_Religious_Violence_in_Minecraft |archive-date=2019-11-24 |access-date=December 6, 2019 |dead-url=no }}{{unreliable source?|date=February 2020}}</ref><ref name="rps">{{Cite news |last=Caldwell |first=Brendan |url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/02/29/minecrafts-most-obscene-server/ |title=Ridealong: The Ruin Of Minecraft's Most Obscene Server |date=February 29, 2016 |work=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]] |access-date=September 11, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014212539/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/02/29/minecrafts-most-obscene-server/ |archive-date=2019-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=vice/><ref name="ign">{{Cite news |last=Craig |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/20/the-6-most-amazing-things-ive-seen-in-minecraft |title=The 6 Most Amazing Things I've Seen in Minecraft |date=June 20, 2013 |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=September 9, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528205653/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/20/the-6-most-amazing-things-ive-seen-in-minecraft |archive-date=2019-05-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而且無封禁的威脅<ref name="celebspulse"/>。伺服器的預設難度是「困難」，[[PvP|PvP]]一直生效<ref name="pcgamesn2012">{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcgamesn.com/minecraft/2b2t-photodiary-inside-minecrafts-most-offensive-server |title=2b2t photodiary: Inside Minecraft's most offensive server |last=Pearson |first=Craig |date=June 3, 2012 |website={{tsl|en|PCGamesN|}} |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609025453/http://www.pcgamesn.com/minecraft/2b2t-photodiary-inside-minecrafts-most-offensive-server |archive-date=2012-06-09 |access-date=December 26, 2019 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至今，伺服器有超過58萬玩家的記錄，存档大小超過13.3TB。<ref name=subreddit/>新聞媒體把2b2t描述為《我的世界》最惡劣的伺服器，歸因於它的玩家社群和文化。

